{"tid":1329814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721戰術篇] 勇武和理非同我入黎討論下到時要點做","createTime":"2019-07-18T10:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:12:38.000Z","uid":153864,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"28a21d1620d5efc01c55ab5a97012d856c9a84cf","tid":1329814,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T10:21:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚好搞終審法院</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚好搞終審法院</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚好搞終審法院</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢一個係最重要嘅前切<br />\n<br />\n和理非行完不撤係後排幫手傳運物資<br />\n咁樣可以為前線爭取好多時間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋 我想問下大家之前咁多次我哋係夏愨道輸乜嘢<br />\n唔夠gear可以同佢地匹敵<br />\n咁大家有冇諗過一啲戰術可以係冇gear嘅情況底下作戰？<br />\n例如一齊撤退完之後喺其他地方再起哄？<br />\n有冇諗過睇夏愨道輸咗咁多次<br />\n對面都已經知道有咩路線可以增援<br />\n要明白戰線唔一定單單呢一條<br />\n佢哋已經熟悉左地理優勢<br />\n好快可以調配狗力<br />\n<br />\n下面自由討論<br />\n我希望大家都可以得到一啲共識<br />\n有啲乜嘢戰術係可以令到我哋可以成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.21見<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩幫我推上去<br />\n唔好再比班3毛係熱門到猖狂<br />\n大戰將到 721先應該係我哋嘅重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water</span></span>"},{"pid":"246be87d2d9a1be99c91988063e35495e1a5937f","tid":1329814,"uid":153864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0